NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|One choice is "top of nothing" when you lead the top card. The advantage is partner knows you do not have an honor. That happens to work well on this hand. The disadvantage is partner does not know whether you have two or three. I believe that top of nothing is the most popular choice, although I am not 100% sure. Regardless, that is what I play.
|
