NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The second choice is low from three small cards. I like count leads, as I like to count out the hand, as those of you who took my recent lesson know. But, then sometimes I can't tell if pard has an honor. So, it has plusses and minuses as well.|
