NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The third choice is what is known as "MUD" which stands for "middle up down." In this hand, Patti leads the three (middle), then plays the six, and then the two. That is my least favorite choice because you often can't tell if pard has an honor or is leading MUD--you know neither count nor attitude. My recommendation is to pick either high or low.|
